            </h2>  

        <ul class="job-key-info">

<li><span class="jkey-title">Job Type</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href="/jobs-by-type/contract">Contract</a></span></li>

<li><span class="jkey-title">Qualification</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href="/jobs-by-education/matric">Matric</a></span></li>

<li><span class="jkey-title">Experience</span> <span class="jkey-info">5 years</span></li>

<li><span class="jkey-title">Location</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href='/jobs-location/kwazulu-natal'>KwaZulu-Natal</a></span></li>


<li><span class="jkey-title">Job Field</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href="/jobs-by-field/administration">Administration / Facilities</a>&nbsp</span>

</li>


</ul>

<div class="job-details">


<p>Key Responsibilities</p>

<ul>
	<li>Supervise regulating activity</li>
	<li>Oversee plant, Equipment and Material requirements</li>
	<li>Supervision of team members</li>
	<li>Accepts responsibility for Safety, Health, Environment, and Quality compliance</li>
	<li>Communication</li>
</ul>

<p>Minimum requirements<br />
Qualification(s):&nbsp;</p>

<ul>
	<li>Grade 12 or equivalent&nbsp;</li>
	<li>Valid driver&rsquo;s license&nbsp;</li>
</ul>

<p>Preferable:&nbsp;</p>

<ul>
	<li>HV Regulations (Modules 1-10)&nbsp;</li>
	<li>Relevant H&amp;S Courses for Supervisors</li>
</ul>

<p>Experience:</p>

<ul>
	<li>5 years&rsquo; experience in supervising the overall regulating activities of Transmission Line Construction&nbsp;</li>
	<li>Construction and Authorised (HV Regulations) Supervisory working experience&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
<p>

<a class="anko-a tc-bl" href="javascript:;" onClick="document.getElementById('application-method').scrollIntoView()">go to method of application »</a>

</p>


</div>

        <h2  class="mag-b " id="job1251298">

            
            <a href='/job/team-leader-construction-port-shepstone-kzn-eskom-communications' class='subjob-title'>Team Leader Construction - Port Shepstone KZN </a>


            </h2>  

        <ul class="job-key-info">

<li><span class="jkey-title">Job Type</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href="/jobs-by-type/full-time">Full Time</a></span></li>

<li><span class="jkey-title">Qualification</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href="/jobs-by-education/matric">Matric</a></span></li>

<li><span class="jkey-title">Experience</span> <span class="jkey-info">2 years</span></li>

<li><span class="jkey-title">Location</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href='/jobs-location/kwazulu-natal'>KwaZulu-Natal</a></span></li>


<li><span class="jkey-title">Job Field</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href="/jobs-by-field/building-and-construction">Construction and Site Engineering</a>&nbsp</span>

</li>


</ul>

<div class="job-details">


<p>Key Responsibilities</p>

<ul>
	<li>Assist in overseeing the civils activity</li>
	<li>Assisting the Supervisor in assessing job priorities and assigning employees to appropriate job sites.</li>
	<li>Give clear direction to workers to ensure that daily objectives are met.</li>
	<li>Accepts responsibility for plant, equipment and material.</li>
	<li>Informs supervisor of the required plant, tools and equipment.</li>
	<li>Check tools and equipment is available and in good working condition.</li>
	<li>Support the supervisor with Safety, Health and Environmental requirements.</li>
	<li>Communication &ndash; daily feedback to the supervisor on progress as well as on any difficulties or problems that might be experienced.</li>
	<li>Complete and submit documentation as required</li>
</ul>

<p>Qualification(s):</p>

<ul>
	<li>Grade 12 (Matric) or equivalent</li>
	<li>Driver&rsquo;s license</li>
	<li>ORHVS</li>
	<li>Relevant Civil Qualification would be an added advantage</li>
</ul>

<p>Experience:</p>

<ul>
	<li>2- years relevant experience in Leading Regulating Activities on Civils</li>
</ul>
<p>

<a class="anko-a tc-bl" href="javascript:;" onClick="document.getElementById('application-method').scrollIntoView()">go to method of application »</a>

</p>


</div>

